.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
House: ranch-style, townhouse, wooden, cottage, art-deco
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, dubstep, funk, classical
1. the ranch-style house is the person who likes red
2. the swedish house is the fan of dubstep
3. the townhouse house is the person drinking tea
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the fan of reggae
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the cottage house is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of jazz
11. the fan of classicals is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the wooden house is the prince-smoker
14. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| House	|   cottage	|    townhouse	|    ranch-style	|    wooden	|    swedish	|
| Music-Genre		|     jazz	|    classical	|     reggae	|     funk	|      dubstep	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
